<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Go to Question Format</title>
  <!-- Font Awesome -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
  <!-- Google Fonts -->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #1E90FF; /* Sky blue */
      --primary-light: #87CEEB;
      --primary-dark: #0078D7;
      --secondary: #8B4513; /* Brown */
      --secondary-light: #A67C52;
      --secondary-dark: #5D2E0D;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --gray-50: #f9fafb;
      --gray-100: #f3f4f6;
      --gray-200: #e5e7eb;
      --gray-300: #d1d5db;
      --gray-600: #4b5563;
      --gray-700: #374151;
      --shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #87CEEB 0%, #1E90FF 50%, #4682B4 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: var(--gray-700);
      line-height: 1.6;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    
    .container {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 500px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease;
    }
    
    .container::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 6px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
    }
    
    .icon {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      background: rgba(30, 144, 255, 0.1);
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      color: var(--secondary);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    
    p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--gray-600);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.85rem 1.75rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary), var(--secondary-dark));
      color: var(--white);
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.3);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.4);
    }
    
    .btn:active {
      transform: translateY(1px);
      box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.3);
    }
    
    .btn::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: -100%;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.2), transparent);
      transition: left 0.6s ease;
    }
    
    .btn:hover::before {
      left: 100%;
    }
    
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 576px) {
      .container {
        padding: 2rem;
        max-width: 90%;
      }
      
      h1 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }
      
      p {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
      
      .icon {
        font-size: 3rem;
        width: 80px;
        height: 80px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="icon">
      <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i>
    </div>
    <h1>Question Format Not Set</h1>
    <p>Dear Teacher, the subject question format has not been set up yet. Please set it up first to continue.</p>
    <a href="/admin/subject" class="btn">
      <i class="fas fa-cog"></i>
      Set Question Format Now
    </a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>